{"tid":1126390,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"新科技，新 iPad Pro 或支援滑鼠操作！","createTime":"2019-04-26T10:56:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-27T06:55:33.000Z","uid":50534,"like":0,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"ba3490f71cc18af76383acdfa7215124d451c036","tid":1126390,"uid":50534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T10:56:36.000Z","msg":"Apple 策略繼續大倒退？新 iPad Pro 或支援滑鼠操作！<br />\nBy Marco - 4 月 26, 2019<br />\nApple 一直以辦公工具深入人心，特別是在 MacBook 或者 iMac 產品上得到完美展現。而在近年，Apple 為了提升 iPad Pro 相對薄弱的辦公性能上花了心思去升級，但還是缺少些什麼，其中的一個難題可能就是滑鼠操控。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現時 iPad 已經增加了 Smart Keyboard、Apple Pencil 等支援，可以極大的提高iPad 的生產力。而根據外媒的爆料，Apple 或許將在後續為 iPad Pro 新增支援滑鼠「即插即用」功能，而且為此將會在最新一代 iPad Pro 上罕見地將 Lightning 接口改為 Type C 接口，目的就是為了能更好的兼容 USB 滑鼠等外設。<br />\n<br />\n對於該消息是否屬實，Apple 最快會於今年六月的 WWDC 開發者大會上介紹 iOS 13 時宣布此功能。<br />\n如果 Apple 真的加入了這個新功能，有了滑鼠功能的 iPad，相信會為一些習慣了鼠標操控的用戶帶了便利，讓辦公效率極大的提升。只是，這樣做的話就會失去了當初設計 iPad，作為一部可以取代輕量型手提電腦的目標，產品市場策略上確有大倒退的嫌疑。<br />\n<a href=\"https://qooah.com/2019/04/26/ipad-pro-usb-mouse-support/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fqooah.com%2F2019%2F04%2F26%2Fipad-pro-usb-mouse-support%2F&d=tLsEO8KpRnvfRHW%2FlT3TjvS0i%2BS8%2FYHgnNJfWlbrK%2Bw%3D&h=58afc216\" target=\"_blank\">https://qooah.com/2019/04/26/ipad-pro-usb-mouse-support/</a>"},{"pid":"6eed453d2b85938013d26812ca19e0d34e7064fe","tid":1126390,"uid":12628,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T10:58:34.000Z","msg":"隻老鼠一定好撚柒貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27cab604fb84a7c38cd89fa5531030d396ce0a87","tid":1126390,"uid":216877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T11:05:33.000Z","msg":"藍芽mouse用唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5099d9290301bbdfce20f9e568a95bfb5a3340d9","tid":1126390,"uid":841